Served as a Director on the Board of Directors of the Graduate Student Association at the University of Waterloo from April 2021 to April 2023.

Participated in board meetings and discussions related to graduate student affairs, governance, student services, and community initiatives. Contributed to policy revision, decision-making processes and supported activities aimed at improving graduate student experience and engagement at the university.
